import { Component } from '@angular/core'; import { ActivatedRoute } from '@angular/router'; import { LibrarylogService } from '../librarylog.service'; @Component({ selector: 'app-viewstudents', templateUrl: './viewstudents.component.html', styleUrls: ['./viewstudents.component.css'] }) export class ViewstudentsComponent { activeroute: any; constructor(activeroute: ActivatedRoute) { } studid:any; ngOnInit(): void { this.activeroute.paramMap.subscribe((params: { get: (arg0: string) => any; }) =>{ this.studid = params.get('eid'); console.log(this.studid); }) } }
